snippet.title: Classic Clicks
snippet.description:
Hello Friends!

First of all I would like to thank you all for visiting Classic Clicks.

Our channel is all about Rare and Common, Pictures / Clips of Living and Non Living personalities. Their lifestyle, family, friends, performance etc. 
We have also added rare and common pictures of Places, Funny things around the world, Historic events  etc.

The content provided to you is collected from Internet and is not meant to offend any living or non living person.  Regarding any issue with the posted content please feel free to add your comment in channel's discussion tab.

We would have not make it so far without your support. I want to thank you all again for being our esteem and wonderful viewers and subscribers.

If you have not subscribed yet, please subscribe to our channel and keep liking and sharing the videos.

Thank You!
